---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About | June Kato" description="Learn more about June Kato, a freelance illustrator creating vibrant, character-driven artwork for books, brands, and editorial projects.">
  <!-- About Hero -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-50 to-white py-20 sm:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 tracking-tight">
        About me
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Hi, I'm June Kato—a freelance illustrator with a passion for bringing stories to life through vibrant, character-driven artwork.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- My Story Section -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">My story</h2>
      <div class="prose prose-lg text-gray-600 space-y-4">
        <p>
          I've been drawing for as long as I can remember. What started as doodles in the margins of my school notebooks eventually grew into a full-fledged career. After studying illustration and working with various clients over the years, I decided to go freelance to focus on the projects I'm most passionate about.
        </p>
        <p>
          My work is inspired by everyday moments, nature, and the small details that make each story unique. I believe that great illustration doesn't just decorate—it communicates, evokes emotion, and connects with people on a deeper level.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What I Do Section -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-24 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">What I do</h2>
      <div class="prose prose-lg text-gray-600 space-y-4">
        <p>
          I specialize in creating illustrations for books, editorial publications, and brands. Whether it's a whimsical children's book cover, a thought-provoking magazine piece, or custom artwork for your business, I approach every project with care and attention to detail.
        </p>
        <p>
          My process always begins with pencil sketches—there's something about that hand-drawn foundation that gives digital work warmth and personality. From there, I refine and polish until we have something that truly captures your vision.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Let's Work Together Section -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Let's work together</h2>
      <div class="prose prose-lg text-gray-600 space-y-4">
        <p>
          I'm always excited to take on new projects and collaborate with creative teams, publishers, and businesses. If you have an idea you'd like to explore or a project that needs illustration, I'd love to hear from you.
        </p>
        <p>
          You can check out some of my recent work on the <a href="/#work" class="text-gray-900 underline hover:text-gray-700">homepage</a>, or feel free to <a href="mailto:hello@junekato.com" class="text-gray-900 underline hover:text-gray-700">get in touch</a> directly. Let's make something beautiful together.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
